<item>
            <title>[LU-15681] crash in lnet_process_id_hash()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15681</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Dear Devs,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;During heavy workload we are experiencing kernel crash caused by page fault in &#160;lnet_process_id_hash()&lt;/p&gt;

